headline: AI and momentum trades are getting too crowded, blue chips may be the way to go: JPMorgan
summary: JPMorgan recommends Coca-Cola over Coinbase, citing an overextended and risky AI-driven market rally.

headline: Insights Into Allegion (ALLE) Q2: Wall Street Projections for Key Metrics
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Allegion (ALLE), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended June 2025.
